{"tid":1141424,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"樓市爆煲！！！業主逆市即減32萬沽映灣園！！！","createTime":"2019-05-06T12:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T01:13:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4d1d722be76e27e17e5332918bbd56dc56d098c9","tid":1141424,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yK7Q2t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yK7Q2t.png&h=9993d62c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易談判現變數，港股及內地A股周一(6日)暴瀉，連帶樓市交投亦即時受影響。中原陳旭明表示，東涌映灣園15座低層D室連租約三房戶，實用面積645方呎，現時以1.7萬元租出。 <br />\n<br />\n業主原本堅持叫價760萬元，但今日(6日)見股市波動，外圍走向未明，立即減價32萬元，將單位以728萬沽出，實用呎價11,287元。上址2016年2月購入價550萬元，是次轉售帳面獲利178萬元。"},{"pid":"411d9fe223c1ca028d01ee75761e3f3376823275","tid":1141424,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友由未來世界嚟，佢話香港樓市即將大爆煲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1140806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1140806</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"363d54aa5ea56d4ee6d58e48094dd96083decca3","tid":1141424,"uid":182330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:01:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b31a8c9b47bbbce632c17938af52d34bfd301fb7","tid":1141424,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"好快會後悔"},{"pid":"e963c68dec5cd758cb5167cb747e09c701a50109","tid":1141424,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"今次堅爆"},{"pid":"038e5623a7cefb2be9811c2f4f3d6ea4d9ba551d","tid":1141424,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"32萬好少野,咪當送裝修"},{"pid":"2159b4cbd290a733c7111842097ff13acb1719de","tid":1141424,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b31a8c9b47bbbce632c17938af52d34bfd301fb7","tid":1141424,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"r